WEBVTT

00:52.030 --> 00:52.840
My legs are numb.

00:53.590 --> 00:54.430
Don't move.

00:54.810 --> 00:55.360
Let me help you.

00:56.430 --> 00:58.110
You're really something, Shen Xifan.

00:58.790 --> 01:00.100
You can't sleep well,

01:00.470 --> 01:01.620
yet you came to sleep on the yoga mat

01:01.640 --> 01:03.280
instead of sleeping in bed.

01:03.640 --> 01:05.930
I thought since I couldn't sleep anyway,

01:05.960 --> 01:07.350
I should get up and exercise.

01:07.370 --> 01:09.010
It's healthier this way.

01:10.039 --> 01:10.789
Alright.

01:10.789 --> 01:12.230
Just sleep here then.

01:12.510 --> 01:13.070
Mom.

01:14.400 --> 01:15.510
I'm hungry.

01:16.120 --> 01:17.350
Well, I don't know how to cook.

01:17.870 --> 01:18.760
Mr. Shen.

01:18.960 --> 01:19.990
Get up. Time to work.

01:31.870 --> 01:32.759
Look how sleepy you are.

01:32.759 --> 01:34.120
How many hours did you sleep last night?

01:34.789 --> 01:35.840
Last night...

01:36.630 --> 01:37.870
From 1 a.m. to 3 a.m.,

01:37.870 --> 01:39.070
and then from 5 a.m. to 6 a.m.

01:39.229 --> 01:39.960
Only a few hours.

01:39.960 --> 01:40.789
Come on, eat this.

01:40.789 --> 01:41.229
Gosh.

01:41.229 --> 01:43.039
You only slept for less than five hours.

01:43.229 --> 01:43.960
Give me the bowl.

01:43.960 --> 01:45.200
Did you take melatonin?

01:45.680 --> 01:46.229
Yes.

01:46.229 --> 01:46.920
It didn't work.

01:47.229 --> 01:49.120
What should we do?

01:49.120 --> 01:50.509
We've tried everything, including sleep aid spray

01:50.509 --> 01:51.400
and fragrance.

01:51.400 --> 01:52.350
Nothing worked.

01:52.350 --> 01:53.320
Talking about tax on stupidity.

01:53.920 --> 01:54.600
You're just a manager of

01:54.600 --> 01:56.229
the Front Office Department of a hotel.

01:56.229 --> 01:57.509
Do you have to work so hard?

01:57.960 --> 01:58.840
You have trouble sleeping every day.

01:58.990 --> 01:59.870
I'm worried you'll have a
physical breakdown.

02:00.960 --> 02:01.920
How about

02:02.230 --> 02:03.480
I go get some sleeping pills?

02:03.480 --> 02:04.480
Sleeping pills won't do.

02:04.990 --> 02:05.790
They'll cause damage to your brain.

02:06.320 --> 02:08.229
But chronic sleep deprivation will also cause damage to my brain.

02:10.110 --> 02:11.070
Why did you kick me?

02:12.320 --> 02:12.920
My legs are short.

02:12.920 --> 02:13.390
I kicked the wrong person.

02:13.390 --> 02:14.350
You did it on purpose, didn't you?

02:14.350 --> 02:15.160
No. No.

02:15.160 --> 02:16.720
Ms. Shen, why don't you

02:16.720 --> 02:18.000
go see a TCM physician

02:18.000 --> 02:19.670
and let him or her prescribe some traditional Chinese medicine for you to recuperate?

02:20.790 --> 02:21.480
TCM is good.

02:21.790 --> 02:22.829
I remember they said

02:22.829 --> 02:23.950
in the neighborhood group chat that

02:23.950 --> 02:25.630
there's a TCM clinic nearby.

02:25.630 --> 02:26.829
There's an expert

02:26.829 --> 02:28.670
who specializes in treating insomnia for the elderly.

02:28.670 --> 02:30.200
But I'm young.

02:30.200 --> 02:31.920
My insomnia is not the same as the elderly's, okay?

02:31.920 --> 02:33.600
As the saying goes, we can treat a dead horse as if it were still alive.

02:34.160 --> 02:35.160
Fine.

02:35.160 --> 02:35.950
This dead horse here

02:35.950 --> 02:38.070
will go receive the treatment after finishing this egg.

02:40.070 --> 02:41.280
Guess I'll have to get it over with.

02:43.160 --> 02:45.660
[The Best Thing]

02:46.010 --> 02:49.820
[Episode 1 Suye]
[Tastes pungent, is warm in nature, relieves the exterior and dispels the cold, promotes the flow of qi and gastric motility]

02:51.610 --> 02:56.000
[Spring]

03:38.490 --> 03:40.270
[Hong'an Gate]

03:53.079 --> 03:53.920
Here's my prescription.

03:58.220 --> 04:00.540
My joints, right here.

04:01.040 --> 04:03.760
And my knees. They hurt every spring.

04:09.000 --> 04:10.110
I cough a lot at night.

04:10.420 --> 04:10.980
Hello.

04:11.510 --> 04:12.040
Hello.

04:12.040 --> 04:13.200
Do you want to make an appointment?

04:13.880 --> 04:14.350
Yes.

04:14.350 --> 04:15.830
I suffer from insomnia.

04:16.040 --> 04:17.480
Okay, this way please.

04:17.790 --> 04:18.640
Okay, thank you.

04:21.040 --> 04:22.840
[He Suye]

04:22.860 --> 04:24.430
[TCM Consulting Room 3]

04:28.580 --> 04:29.960
[Hong'an Gate Outpatient Department]

04:29.350 --> 04:30.160
Since I'm already here,

04:30.640 --> 04:31.720
I may as well give it a try.

04:32.790 --> 04:34.480
It's still a little cold in April.

04:34.480 --> 04:35.190
Keep yourself warm.

04:35.190 --> 04:35.990
Okay.

04:37.750 --> 04:38.400
Sorry.

04:38.670 --> 04:39.430
Did the door hit you?

04:42.080 --> 04:42.790
No.

04:42.790 --> 04:43.670
I'm sorry.

04:46.040 --> 04:46.600
Uncle.

04:46.920 --> 04:47.790
Give the prescription

04:47.790 --> 04:48.670
to the lady over there

04:48.670 --> 04:49.520
and pay the bill.

04:50.110 --> 04:50.840
Thank you.

04:51.159 --> 04:52.080
Xiangya.Xiangya.

04:52.230 --> 04:54.870
I found a TCM physician with beautiful eyes.

04:55.230 --> 04:56.110
I think

04:56.110 --> 04:57.280
he's definitely your type.

04:59.430 --> 05:00.110
Is he handsome?

05:02.550 --> 05:04.720
He was wearing a mask, and I didn't see his face clearly.

05:05.790 --> 05:06.680
I have a task for you.

05:06.710 --> 05:08.150
Assess his looks.

05:08.480 --> 05:09.720
Copy that.

05:11.720 --> 05:12.870
Did you make an appointment with me?

05:17.640 --> 05:18.350
Dr. He.

05:19.550 --> 05:20.080
Come on in.

05:25.080 --> 05:26.040
Where do you feel sick?

05:27.350 --> 05:28.350
I suffer from insomnia.

05:28.550 --> 05:29.480
How long has it been?

05:30.280 --> 05:31.720
Quite a while.

05:31.960 --> 05:33.640
I've been taking melatonin lately, but it didn't work.

05:36.350 --> 05:37.280
Insomnia...

05:44.020 --> 05:46.690
[temperament]

05:45.020 --> 05:46.820
He has a pretty good temperament.

05:47.400 --> 05:47.840
Come on.

05:48.110 --> 05:48.640
I'll take your pulse.

05:49.870 --> 05:50.510
Your hand.

05:58.720 --> 06:00.670
His nails are clean too.

05:59.020 --> 06:01.740
[Tidiness]

06:00.960 --> 06:02.550
What time do you usually go to sleep?

06:04.590 --> 06:05.800
quite late, actually.

06:06.520 --> 06:07.520
About...

06:07.520 --> 06:08.310
A little past 1?

06:08.960 --> 06:09.870
A little past 1?

06:10.280 --> 06:11.080
That's too late.

06:12.430 --> 06:13.080
Do you dream a lot?

06:13.750 --> 06:15.190
I do dream quite a lot.

06:15.430 --> 06:16.080
Bad dreams?

06:16.600 --> 06:17.600
All kinds of dreams.

06:18.960 --> 06:20.840
His voice is also pretty decent.

06:19.290 --> 06:24.240
[Voice]

06:20.920 --> 06:23.040
He must be Xiangya's type.

06:23.040 --> 06:23.640
The other hand.

06:28.990 --> 06:29.870
But...

06:29.870 --> 06:32.230
How can I get him to take off his mask?

06:43.750 --> 06:44.960
When your pulse is taken,

06:44.960 --> 06:46.350
you need to stay calm

06:46.350 --> 06:47.670
and not let your mind wander.

06:52.080 --> 06:53.230
I can't hear you clearly.

06:53.230 --> 06:54.550
Why don't you take off your mask

06:54.550 --> 06:55.600
and speak louder?

06:57.480 --> 06:58.230
I said,

06:58.230 --> 07:00.310
don't let your mind wander.

07:06.080 --> 07:06.960
Lift your face up

07:06.960 --> 07:07.870
so I can check your complexion.

07:18.840 --> 07:19.600
Your symptoms are caused by

07:19.750 --> 07:20.920
emotional trauma.

07:21.350 --> 07:22.480
Your worrying does damage to your liver,

07:22.920 --> 07:23.870
heart, and spleen,

07:23.870 --> 07:25.750
which leads to neurasthenia,

07:25.750 --> 07:26.720
restlessness and frequent dreams.

07:27.600 --> 07:28.870
If you want to get healthier,

07:28.870 --> 07:29.960
have less cold food,

07:29.960 --> 07:30.840
iced coffee,

07:30.840 --> 07:32.480
and iced bubble tea.

07:35.960 --> 07:37.480
I'll prescribe some liver-soothing and qi-regulating medicine for you

07:38.430 --> 07:39.670
so that you won't suffer from insomnia and frequent dreams anymore.

07:40.230 --> 07:41.230
But more importantly,

07:41.230 --> 07:42.550
you need to let go of what's on your mind.

07:43.600 --> 07:44.430
Has there been

07:44.430 --> 07:45.140
anything that

07:45.170 --> 07:46.280
makes you upset lately?

07:46.600 --> 07:47.300
For example, work,

07:47.550 --> 07:48.430
or other aspects of life.

07:56.210 --> 07:58.360
I've just been busy with work.

08:00.040 --> 08:01.350
Nothing else, specifically.

08:07.280 --> 08:07.770
It's okay.

08:07.930 --> 08:09.490
I'll prescribe some medicine for you.

08:09.510 --> 08:10.680
It's nothing serious.

08:14.520 --> 08:15.280
Do you know how to decoct medicine?

08:16.840 --> 08:17.520
No.

08:18.350 --> 08:19.110
Then...

08:19.480 --> 08:20.230
Pharmacy decoction it is.

08:29.080 --> 08:30.230
Take this prescription

08:30.790 --> 08:31.920
and pay at the reception desk.

08:32.470 --> 08:33.070
Remember to come again

08:33.070 --> 08:33.919
for a follow-up visit next Saturday.

08:35.520 --> 08:36.590
I need to come again for a follow-up visit?

08:38.000 --> 08:38.669
Okay.

08:38.669 --> 08:40.120
Thank you then.

09:19.120 --> 09:20.000
See you next week.

09:23.000 --> 09:23.640
Hello.

09:23.950 --> 09:24.430
Hello.

09:24.880 --> 09:26.200
Here's the prescription for pharmacy decoction.

09:26.220 --> 09:27.130
Thank you.

09:28.040 --> 09:28.640
Please wait a moment.

09:28.640 --> 09:29.070
Okay.

09:33.280 --> 09:34.120
How did it go?

09:34.120 --> 09:34.880
Did you see his face?

09:37.520 --> 09:39.920
I didn't see his face. Sad.

09:44.470 --> 09:45.310
Miss Shen.

09:46.160 --> 09:47.190
I forgot to remind you.

09:47.400 --> 09:48.670
The pharmacy closes at 5 p.m.

09:49.000 --> 09:49.830
Pharmacy decoction

09:49.830 --> 09:51.600
takes four hours.

09:53.360 --> 09:54.160
So,

09:54.470 --> 09:55.590
you can come and collect your medicine

09:55.590 --> 09:56.550
at 2 p.m.

09:59.160 --> 09:59.790
Okay.

10:12.190 --> 10:13.000
Miss Shen.

10:14.640 --> 10:16.280
Our pharmacy closes at 5 p.m.

10:16.520 --> 10:17.550
Pharmacy decoction

10:17.790 --> 10:19.580
takes four hours.

10:19.920 --> 10:20.590
So,

10:20.880 --> 10:22.430
you can come

10:22.830 --> 10:24.310
and collect your medicine at about 2 p.m.

10:25.430 --> 10:26.550
Thank you.

10:26.970 --> 10:27.720
-Take care.
-Thank you.

10:45.830 --> 10:46.670
If you encounter any trouble

10:46.670 --> 10:47.790
at work,

10:48.240 --> 10:49.400
don't take it to heart.

10:50.470 --> 10:51.760
Don't put too much pressure on yourself.

10:58.280 --> 10:59.470
You're going to study abroad?

11:02.880 --> 11:04.360
You didn't even discuss such an important matter with me.

11:05.120 --> 11:06.040
You've really changed.

11:06.480 --> 11:07.360
I didn't have time to answer the phone,

11:07.360 --> 11:08.640
so you just stopped talking to me?

11:10.580 --> 11:12.250
Are you going to accuse me of not replying to your messages again?

11:14.590 --> 11:15.470
Shen Xifan.

11:15.900 --> 11:17.740
Being your boyfriend is too tiring.

11:18.590 --> 11:19.430
You know how busy I am at work.

11:19.430 --> 11:21.040
Can't you be more considerate of me?

11:25.760 --> 11:26.590
Yan Heng.

11:28.400 --> 11:29.120
Let's

11:29.120 --> 11:30.550
not talk about this today, okay?

11:31.350 --> 11:32.420
We haven't seen each other

11:32.920 --> 11:34.380
for quite a long time.

12:06.590 --> 12:07.540
What are you doing?

12:21.880 --> 12:24.670
Go pay at the information desk later.

12:24.670 --> 12:25.520
-Remember to use your medical insurance.
-Thank you.

12:25.520 --> 12:25.950
It's nothing.

12:25.950 --> 12:26.830
Thank you, doctor.

12:26.830 --> 12:27.470
You're welcome.

12:27.830 --> 12:28.520
Go.

12:28.950 --> 12:29.760
Look, it's over there.

12:29.760 --> 12:30.280
Thank you.

12:30.280 --> 12:30.940
Take care.

12:30.960 --> 12:31.390
Okay.

12:50.710 --> 12:52.790
Remember to come and collect it before 5 p.m.

12:52.790 --> 12:54.430
Otherwise, the pharmacy will close.

12:58.120 --> 12:58.920
Dr. He.

12:59.060 --> 13:00.180
Why are you here?

13:00.240 --> 13:00.920
Anything wrong?

13:02.360 --> 13:03.570
I have no appointment at the moment,

13:03.590 --> 13:04.500
so I came out for a walk.

13:35.710 --> 13:36.640
Dr. He.

13:37.070 --> 13:39.310
You seem to be quite free all day.

13:39.920 --> 13:40.760
It's time for me to get off work.

13:41.510 --> 13:42.390
I'm leaving then.

13:42.420 --> 13:43.910
Okay, see you next week.

13:50.710 --> 13:51.590
Time to get off work,

13:51.590 --> 13:52.640
Dr. Sun.

13:52.790 --> 13:53.430
Okay.

13:58.190 --> 13:58.670
Ms. Shen?

13:59.430 --> 14:00.070
Here.

14:00.070 --> 14:01.710
I got your medicine back for you.

14:01.710 --> 14:02.360
Drink it.

14:07.920 --> 14:08.920
What's wrong?

14:09.950 --> 14:11.400
It's too bitter.

14:11.400 --> 14:11.950
I don't want to drink it.

14:12.310 --> 14:14.550
Bitter medicine is good for the disease.

14:14.550 --> 14:15.760
Haven't you heard of this saying?

14:15.760 --> 14:16.400
Drink it.

14:21.920 --> 14:24.880
Can I really trust the doctor at my neighborhood clinic?

15:02.640 --> 15:03.190
Suye.

15:03.190 --> 15:04.070
Come and save me.

15:04.210 --> 15:08.130
[Jiangzhou Medical University
Affiliated TCM Hospital]

15:15.190 --> 15:16.550
Dr. He, you're finally here.

15:16.790 --> 15:17.280
Come on.

15:17.370 --> 15:19.010
The patient's family was about to scold Li Jie to tears.

15:19.470 --> 15:21.000
Are you good for nothing?

15:21.280 --> 15:22.190
So you're saying,

15:22.190 --> 15:23.520
you have to insert the tube

15:23.520 --> 15:24.640
into his lungs again,

15:24.640 --> 15:25.760
or he'll suffocate to death?

15:26.000 --> 15:26.470
Do you believe

15:26.470 --> 15:27.590
I'll report it to your director and dean?

15:27.590 --> 15:28.360
That's not what I meant.

15:29.190 --> 15:29.640
Dr. He.

15:29.640 --> 15:30.190
Senior He.

15:30.190 --> 15:30.670
Do something.

15:30.670 --> 15:31.310
Calm down.

15:31.310 --> 15:32.070
He can't even breathe now.

15:32.070 --> 15:32.590
Medical record.

15:39.400 --> 15:40.070
Lung cancer.

15:43.950 --> 15:44.430
Tongue.

15:46.790 --> 15:48.520
His tongue coating is thick and greasy, and his tongue is red.

15:48.710 --> 15:49.470
Did you use needles?

15:51.240 --> 15:51.760
Li Jie.

15:52.360 --> 15:52.920
I did.

15:53.550 --> 15:54.640
I inserted a needle into each of

15:54.670 --> 15:55.980
the three acupoints: Feishu, Neiguan, and Fenglong.

15:56.310 --> 15:58.120
The patient has lung cancer combined with infection,

15:58.360 --> 16:00.120
and his respiratory secretions increased and turned into sputum.

16:01.360 --> 16:02.710
The patient is in poor general condition.

16:03.000 --> 16:04.240
Sputum is blocking his airways,

16:04.240 --> 16:05.670
causing breathing difficulties for the patient.

16:06.190 --> 16:07.000
Did he cough up sputum?

16:07.470 --> 16:08.240
A little,

16:08.240 --> 16:09.550
but he still couldn't breathe.

16:09.880 --> 16:11.590
So I suggested using a sputum suction machine.

16:11.590 --> 16:12.920
I'm worried if we delay it any longer...

16:13.160 --> 16:14.550
If I had known that we would have to use a sputum suction machine,

16:14.550 --> 16:15.670
we might as well have gone to a Western hospital.

16:15.670 --> 16:16.710
Why would we have chosen a TCM hospital?

16:17.280 --> 16:17.920
Hey.

16:17.920 --> 16:19.190
What are you waiting for?

16:19.190 --> 16:20.400
The machine is ready, isn't it?

16:20.420 --> 16:20.900
Alright.

16:21.190 --> 16:21.760
Li Jie.

16:21.760 --> 16:22.400
Get ready for cupping.

16:23.360 --> 16:24.310
I said, get ready for cupping.

16:24.310 --> 16:24.760
Okay.

16:26.400 --> 16:27.070
Go get the needle cart.

16:27.380 --> 16:27.870
Okay.

16:28.430 --> 16:29.240
Help the patient up.

16:29.590 --> 16:30.360
Take off his shirt.

17:36.600 --> 17:37.160
Sir.

17:37.400 --> 17:38.120
Are you breathing better now?

17:38.400 --> 17:39.360
Much better.

17:39.670 --> 17:40.600
Thank you.

17:40.600 --> 17:41.510
Fortunately, you coughed up the sputum.

17:42.080 --> 17:43.320
Please take a rest.

17:43.430 --> 17:44.510
Thank you, Dr. He.

17:45.270 --> 17:46.800
It's all thanks to you, who came here in the middle of the night.

17:47.230 --> 17:48.670
I was almost scared to death.

17:49.030 --> 17:50.470
I thought he was going to be like my dad,

17:50.470 --> 17:51.600
who had difficulty breathing

17:51.880 --> 17:53.030
and suffocated to death.

17:53.470 --> 17:55.120
Dr. Li also did the right thing inserting the needles.

17:55.120 --> 17:56.430
He bought time for us.

17:56.640 --> 17:58.570
He didn't dare to use the sputum suction machine

17:58.590 --> 18:00.630
because the patient is aged.

18:26.120 --> 18:30.810
[The patient needs to be observed for a while longer. I'll be on duty tonight. Don't worry.]

18:26.120 --> 18:30.810
[What happened today is common. Don't take it to heart.]

18:30.970 --> 18:34.130
[Okay, thank you, Suye.]

18:53.470 --> 18:54.750
I wonder if she'll come

18:54.770 --> 18:55.850
next week for the follow-up visit.

19:24.670 --> 19:25.320
Shen Xifan.

19:26.100 --> 19:27.540
Being your boyfriend is too tiring.

19:28.640 --> 19:29.950
You don't care about me at all.

19:30.120 --> 19:31.360
You only care about yourself.

19:33.060 --> 19:34.370
Only I can put up with you.

19:35.160 --> 19:36.120
Think about it yourself.

20:05.710 --> 20:06.400
A rice ball,

20:06.400 --> 20:06.990
and an egg.

20:08.650 --> 20:09.500
How much is this soy milk?

20:10.950 --> 20:11.470
I'll have one.

20:12.470 --> 20:12.880
Okay.

20:13.320 --> 20:13.710
Thank you.

20:14.920 --> 20:15.430
What would you like to eat?

20:15.990 --> 20:16.640
Boss.

20:16.640 --> 20:18.750
I want a bowl of meat wonton,

20:18.750 --> 20:19.920
one rice ball,

20:19.920 --> 20:21.430
three tea eggs,

20:21.430 --> 20:23.430
a pot of steamed buns,

20:23.430 --> 20:24.750
and three fried dough sticks.

20:25.230 --> 20:25.710
Okay.

20:25.880 --> 20:26.560
Just a moment.

20:26.940 --> 20:27.540
It'll be ready soon.

20:29.360 --> 20:30.320
Where are you?

20:33.080 --> 20:35.470
Ms. Liu. I couldn't sleep,

20:35.510 --> 20:36.950
so I came down to buy breakfast.

20:37.470 --> 20:38.670
I don't know why,

20:38.670 --> 20:40.430
but that traditional Chinese medicine didn't work at all.

20:40.430 --> 20:42.320
I couldn't sleep until three o'clock last night.

20:42.990 --> 20:43.670
How about

20:44.190 --> 20:45.320
you throw it away for me?

20:45.320 --> 20:46.470
What a waste that would be.

20:46.950 --> 20:47.430
Oh my god.

20:48.540 --> 20:49.340
Dr. He.

20:50.710 --> 20:52.230
Traditional Chinese medicine conditioning takes time.

20:52.470 --> 20:53.600
You've only taken one pack.

20:53.600 --> 20:54.880
How could it take effect so quickly?

20:56.950 --> 20:57.510
Right.

20:57.920 --> 20:59.430
I was too anxious.

21:01.310 --> 21:01.790
Here.

21:02.230 --> 21:03.030
Your breakfast is ready.

21:03.050 --> 21:03.680
Thank you.

21:03.950 --> 21:04.270
Okay.

21:07.850 --> 21:08.570
I've transferred the money to you.

21:08.600 --> 21:09.490
Okay, bye.

21:39.860 --> 21:41.140
Dr. He. You just got off the night shift?

21:41.500 --> 21:42.580
I'll have the usual set.

21:42.780 --> 21:43.260
Okay.

21:43.280 --> 21:44.190
The usual set, right?

21:47.640 --> 21:48.230
Boss.

21:48.790 --> 21:50.070
Does that girl come here often?

21:50.910 --> 21:52.110
She lives in this neighborhood too.

21:52.140 --> 21:53.420
She comes here to buy breakfast sometimes.

21:55.320 --> 21:55.640
Okay.

22:01.120 --> 22:01.560
Here you go.

22:02.410 --> 22:02.860
Thank you.

22:03.230 --> 22:03.670
Come again.

22:03.670 --> 22:04.160
Okay.

22:09.670 --> 22:10.640
Here.

22:10.640 --> 22:12.030
Time to take your traditional Chinese medicine.

22:12.990 --> 22:14.600
I don't want to take it.

22:14.600 --> 22:15.750
It's too bitter, and it doesn't work.

22:15.750 --> 22:16.400
Drink it.

22:16.920 --> 22:18.150
Listen.

22:18.320 --> 22:20.360
I ran into that TCM physician downstairs today.

22:20.360 --> 22:21.710
He was also yawning.

22:21.920 --> 22:22.840
You want a person with insomnia

22:22.840 --> 22:24.080
to treat another person with insomnia?

22:24.080 --> 22:25.230
Of course it won't work.

22:25.230 --> 22:25.880
I'm not drinking it.

22:26.640 --> 22:28.560
This is traditional Chinese medicine, not poison.

22:29.270 --> 22:30.270
There's rock candy here.

22:30.600 --> 22:31.360
How's Yan been?

22:31.470 --> 22:32.600
Why haven't I heard about him lately?

22:33.270 --> 22:34.710
He recently started a business.

22:34.710 --> 22:35.600
He must be busy.

22:37.160 --> 22:38.400
Then take the initiative

22:38.880 --> 22:40.190
to care about him.

22:40.800 --> 22:41.880
I know.

22:54.680 --> 22:58.140
[Gunan Huating Manor]

23:13.400 --> 23:15.230
[Gunan Huating Manor]

23:15.430 --> 23:17.120
The Sakura Goddess Set we launched this time

23:17.120 --> 23:18.160
has received great feedback.

23:18.160 --> 23:18.990
Many internet celebrities and public figures

23:18.990 --> 23:19.920
have come to our restaurant

23:19.920 --> 23:21.160
and our executive lounge for a visit.

23:21.160 --> 23:22.360
We've attracted many new customers.

23:22.920 --> 23:23.920
Food & Beverage, you've been collaborating

23:23.920 --> 23:24.920
pretty well with the Marketing Department.

23:27.230 --> 23:27.950
Today, four of our

23:27.950 --> 23:29.080
VIP customers will come to our hotel.

23:29.190 --> 23:29.560
Ding Wei.

23:29.560 --> 23:31.080
Get ready to receive them

23:31.080 --> 23:32.030
at their due time of arrival.

23:33.190 --> 23:33.920
Front Office.

23:33.920 --> 23:35.030
Share the current situation

23:35.030 --> 23:35.710
of these VIP customers

23:35.710 --> 23:36.510
and keep everyone updated.

23:36.670 --> 23:37.080
Okay.

23:37.510 --> 23:38.640
Today, we're scheduled to receive

23:38.640 --> 23:39.840
four VIP customers.

23:39.840 --> 23:41.120
The condition of their rooms has been confirmed.

23:41.120 --> 23:42.120
They can check in at any time.

23:42.320 --> 23:44.640
Among them, Mr. Jiang is a VVIP.

23:44.640 --> 23:46.360
He will bring two assistants with him.

23:46.360 --> 23:48.510
His flight arrives at 3 p.m.,

23:48.510 --> 23:50.160
and he'll arrive at our hotel at about 3:30 p.m.

23:50.400 --> 23:51.470
But it should be noted that

23:51.470 --> 23:52.990
Mr. Jiang is allergic to seafood.

23:52.990 --> 23:53.920
So we need to be careful

23:53.920 --> 23:54.750
when preparing food for him.

23:56.180 --> 23:57.420
He's allergic to seafood?

23:57.500 --> 23:58.060
Okay.

23:58.090 --> 23:59.530
Take note, Food & Beverage.

23:59.560 --> 23:59.950
Alright?

23:59.950 --> 24:01.400
Keep this in mind.

24:01.400 --> 24:01.750
Don't forget...

24:01.750 --> 24:04.120
General Manager. I have some problems to deal with.

24:04.120 --> 24:04.840
I need to go outside for a moment.

24:04.840 --> 24:05.430
Go ahead.

24:05.430 --> 24:05.840
Okay.

24:06.320 --> 24:07.160
Charge my phone for me.

24:07.640 --> 24:08.920
Food & Beverage, take note of

24:08.920 --> 24:10.030
his seafood allergy.

24:10.030 --> 24:10.400
Okay.

24:20.140 --> 24:20.920
Hello.

24:20.950 --> 24:21.880
Pardon me.

24:21.880 --> 24:23.360
I'm Shen Xifan, the Front Office manager.

24:23.360 --> 24:24.640
We'll solve your problem for you right away.

24:24.590 --> 24:25.910
[Front Office]

24:47.950 --> 24:49.260
[Yan Heng]

24:56.840 --> 24:58.950
I forgot to charge my phone yesterday.

24:59.360 --> 25:00.190
I just charged it.

25:00.950 --> 25:01.990
Are you in a meeting?

25:02.600 --> 25:04.670
Reply when you see my message.

25:56.850 --> 25:57.730
This pancake is really good, isn't it?

25:57.750 --> 25:58.830
It was specially saved for us.

26:00.120 --> 26:00.670
Nothing for you.

26:01.560 --> 26:02.190
Why?

26:02.190 --> 26:03.670
I bought bubble tea for the three of us.

26:04.750 --> 26:06.560
You're already undergoing middle-age spread.

26:06.560 --> 26:07.510
Stop eating.

26:07.510 --> 26:08.430
Which one of your eyes saw me

26:08.430 --> 26:09.840
undergoing middle-age spread?

26:10.600 --> 26:10.990
Besides,

26:10.990 --> 26:12.710
part of the success of your Sakura Goddess Set

26:12.020 --> 26:14.440
[Xiangya's Food Diary]

26:12.710 --> 26:13.800
should be attributed to me, okay?

26:14.920 --> 26:17.920
When you took photos with those female internet celebrities,

26:17.920 --> 26:19.710
you grinned from ear to ear.

26:19.710 --> 26:20.400
Bro.

26:20.640 --> 26:21.750
You are a PR manager of the Marketing Department,

26:21.750 --> 26:22.710
not a gigolo.

26:23.120 --> 26:25.160
You are really heartless.

26:25.640 --> 26:27.470
If it weren't for helping you,

26:27.470 --> 26:28.670
would I have taken photos for them?

26:30.030 --> 26:30.360
What's wrong?

26:30.360 --> 26:30.920
Is it bitter?

26:32.990 --> 26:34.030
Have some bubble tea.

26:35.750 --> 26:36.600
I can't.

26:36.600 --> 26:37.670
My TCM physician asked me

26:37.670 --> 26:39.190
to stop drinking tea and coffee.

26:39.190 --> 26:39.990
I can't drink it.

26:40.840 --> 26:42.990
Is milk tea tea? It's milk.

26:44.160 --> 26:44.640
Drink it.

26:46.710 --> 26:47.430
You're right.

26:50.470 --> 26:51.080
Well,

26:51.430 --> 26:53.750
what does that TCM physician you mentioned to me last time look like?

26:58.400 --> 26:59.670
Have you seen "My Journey to You?"

27:00.270 --> 27:01.640
He looks a lot like

27:01.640 --> 27:03.800
the actor who plays Gong Ziyu in that drama.

27:04.030 --> 27:05.400
Really?

27:05.400 --> 27:06.360
Yes.

27:06.360 --> 27:07.320
Do you have a photo?

27:09.230 --> 27:09.880
No.

27:10.080 --> 27:11.750
His photo is not on the expert column.

27:13.190 --> 27:14.030
But Xiangya,

27:14.360 --> 27:14.990
that guy

27:14.990 --> 27:16.510
is definitely your type.

27:17.080 --> 27:18.320
His face

27:18.320 --> 27:19.710
is so handsome that even a passing ant

27:19.710 --> 27:20.950
would be amazed.

27:21.400 --> 27:22.400
I'm going there again for a follow-up visit this Saturday.

27:22.400 --> 27:22.950
Do you want to join me?

27:22.950 --> 27:23.640
Sure.

27:24.190 --> 27:31.990
[Follow-up visit on Saturday
Hong'an Gate Clinic]

27:55.890 --> 27:56.580
What are you looking at?

28:00.120 --> 28:01.840
The smell of traditional Chinese medicine is terrible.

28:02.430 --> 28:03.600
I hope

28:03.600 --> 28:05.080
the handsomeness of that TCM physician

28:05.080 --> 28:06.430
can make me ignore the taste of traditional Chinese medicine.

28:07.750 --> 28:09.430
Beauty, trust me.

28:09.730 --> 28:10.880
Come on.

28:12.850 --> 28:13.530
Let's go.

28:18.330 --> 28:20.240
You're Ms. Shen, Shen Xifan, right?

28:20.540 --> 28:21.060
Yes.

28:22.410 --> 28:24.540
[Expert Yu Liren]

28:30.400 --> 28:32.390
The handsome TCM physician?

28:36.470 --> 28:37.400
I'm sorry.

28:37.710 --> 28:38.950
I must have made the wrong appointment.

28:39.270 --> 28:40.270
I'm here for a follow-up visit.

28:40.270 --> 28:41.190
So I should

28:41.190 --> 28:42.670
see the doctor I saw last time.

28:42.670 --> 28:44.360
You mean Dr. He?

28:44.360 --> 28:44.920
Yes.

28:44.920 --> 28:45.750
Sorry.

28:45.750 --> 28:47.430
He can't make it today.

28:47.990 --> 28:49.710
I'm here on his behalf.

28:51.410 --> 28:52.710
In that case...

28:52.710 --> 28:53.470
What?

28:55.430 --> 28:57.510
You think my medical skills are not as good as his?

28:59.400 --> 29:01.050
That's nonsense.

29:02.160 --> 29:03.400
Since you're here for a follow-up visit,

29:03.400 --> 29:04.320
come on.

29:04.990 --> 29:06.030
Let me take your pulse.

29:08.230 --> 29:09.710
Doctor, examine her carefully.

29:10.270 --> 29:11.270
She's truly sick.

29:16.710 --> 29:17.710
Let me see.

29:18.160 --> 29:19.430
We'll

29:19.600 --> 29:20.400
pay

29:20.990 --> 29:21.510
our bills

29:21.510 --> 29:22.430
over there.

29:23.400 --> 29:24.510
No.

29:25.640 --> 29:27.190
If I take Chinese medicine, I can't drink alcohol anymore.

29:27.190 --> 29:28.030
I won't take it.

29:28.230 --> 29:30.190
Just to make your visit worth it.

29:30.840 --> 29:32.710
The appointment fee was only 30 yuan.

29:32.710 --> 29:33.950
We might as well let it go to waste, okay?

29:33.950 --> 29:34.840
Besides,

29:35.080 --> 29:36.190
I came here to see the handsome guy

29:36.190 --> 29:37.030
and flirt with him.

29:37.030 --> 29:38.670
Do you really think I came here to get TCM treatment?

29:39.750 --> 29:40.990
Go get your medicine. I'll wait for you outside.

29:44.560 --> 29:45.160
Wang Li.

29:45.920 --> 29:46.600
Right.

29:47.470 --> 29:48.910
Why did he stand me up?

29:48.950 --> 29:49.800
Okay, take care.

29:51.040 --> 29:51.470
Here's my prescription.

29:51.500 --> 29:52.630
Let me see.

29:58.230 --> 29:59.990
Did you tell Yan Heng that you were going abroad?

30:03.120 --> 30:04.030
I told him.

30:04.510 --> 30:06.560
He got really mad because of this.

30:07.750 --> 30:08.670
Since then,

30:08.670 --> 30:09.750
he has seldom replied

30:10.360 --> 30:11.950
to my WeChat messages.

30:12.320 --> 30:13.840
And I never had a chance to say it.

30:17.270 --> 30:18.990
Actually, I've always wanted to ask you.

30:20.120 --> 30:21.950
Are you really happy with him?

30:28.320 --> 30:29.160
I don't know.

30:30.320 --> 30:31.400
Maybe

30:32.060 --> 30:33.340
I'm just used to it.

30:35.400 --> 30:37.640
I’ve been together with Yan Heng for too long.

30:38.510 --> 30:39.840
It's been seven whole years.

30:41.120 --> 30:42.120
The two of us

30:42.510 --> 30:43.430
know each other well,

30:44.080 --> 30:45.160
and we're familiar with each other.

30:47.840 --> 30:49.360
It's just I don't know why,

30:50.030 --> 30:50.710
but over the past six months,

30:50.710 --> 30:52.160
we've had fewer and fewer

30:52.160 --> 30:53.230
common topics,

30:53.560 --> 30:55.320
and there's been less and less to talk about.

30:56.230 --> 30:58.270
Did he tell you how many days he'd be away for the business trip?

30:59.400 --> 31:00.710
I told you, I couldn't reach him.

31:23.030 --> 31:23.640
Ling.

31:24.230 --> 31:24.880
Please throw

31:24.880 --> 31:26.470
these flowers and the ones left by the door

31:26.470 --> 31:27.600
away for me.

31:28.120 --> 31:28.800
Okay.

32:33.630 --> 32:35.280
He didn't go to the clinic.

32:36.030 --> 32:37.230
I didn't expect he'd be here.

32:46.570 --> 32:50.160
♫It became brighter because of you♫

32:50.280 --> 32:54.230
♫The world suddenly became so cute♫

32:54.250 --> 32:57.970
♫Maybe I'm too slow to understand♫

32:57.880 --> 32:58.640
Shen Xifan?

32:57.990 --> 33:01.730
♫I can't confess my passionate love to you♫

33:01.920 --> 33:05.730
♫Love is an admiration for beauty♫

33:05.750 --> 33:09.650
♫I've decided to only love you♫

33:07.230 --> 33:08.080
Dr. He.

33:09.670 --> 33:11.670
♫My foolishness♫

33:09.750 --> 33:10.920
You live in this neighborhood too?

33:11.700 --> 33:13.540
♫My sincerity♫

33:11.920 --> 33:12.670
Yes.

33:12.880 --> 33:14.190
This neighborhood is close to the clinic.

33:13.560 --> 33:15.560
♫Only for one person♫

33:14.190 --> 33:15.030
I moved here

33:15.030 --> 33:15.840
for the convenience of seeing patients.

33:19.060 --> 33:21.540
For the convenience of seeing patients...

33:24.290 --> 33:25.330
I did ask you to come to the clinic for a follow-up visit,

33:25.640 --> 33:26.990
but something urgent came up,

33:27.360 --> 33:28.120
so I couldn't make it.

33:28.320 --> 33:28.920
I'm sorry.

33:32.230 --> 33:32.920
Did you

33:32.920 --> 33:34.160
see another doctor?

33:35.320 --> 33:36.670
I did.

33:37.710 --> 33:38.270
That's good.

33:38.700 --> 33:39.150
How about this?

33:39.430 --> 33:39.600
I...

33:39.600 --> 33:41.160
I'll go there again for another follow-up visit next weekend.

33:41.640 --> 33:43.230
Don't stand me up again.

33:43.230 --> 33:44.560
I'm leaving. Enjoy yourself.

33:44.590 --> 33:44.940
Bye.

33:46.190 --> 33:46.640
I...

34:01.800 --> 34:02.750
Next week...

34:07.430 --> 34:14.900
[Sunday]

34:45.239 --> 34:45.949
What wine is this?

34:46.230 --> 34:47.540
This is Professor Yu's favorite.

34:49.710 --> 34:50.239
Grandpa.

34:50.469 --> 34:51.070
I'm back.

34:53.469 --> 34:54.360
Good timing.

34:54.510 --> 34:55.510
Wash your hands and get ready for dinner.

34:55.510 --> 34:56.840
Okay, you guys eat first.

34:56.840 --> 34:57.630
I'll put these on the plate.

35:06.110 --> 35:06.630
Suye.

35:07.030 --> 35:08.950
Can you not tell Grandpa Yu that

35:08.950 --> 35:10.550
I asked you to come to the City Hospital from the clinic

35:10.550 --> 35:12.240
to help me out again yesterday?

35:12.800 --> 35:14.550
I'm worried he'll tell my parents about it,

35:14.550 --> 35:15.940
and my living expenses will be deducted again.

35:16.200 --> 35:17.360
I'll be even poorer.

35:19.200 --> 35:20.110
Don't worry.

35:20.110 --> 35:20.800
Even if I tell him,

35:20.800 --> 35:22.240
I'll be the one to be scolded.

35:24.360 --> 35:25.030
Take it to the table.

35:26.550 --> 35:27.070
Don't tell him.

35:31.070 --> 35:31.510
Here.

35:31.760 --> 35:32.430
The dish is ready.

35:33.200 --> 35:33.760
Let's eat.

35:35.720 --> 35:36.630
Wait.

35:37.430 --> 35:39.320
Fill your glasses first.

35:39.320 --> 35:40.240
Okay.

35:42.070 --> 35:42.470
Here.

35:42.470 --> 35:43.400
Help yourselves.

35:44.150 --> 35:44.630
That's enough.

35:45.070 --> 35:45.760
Thank you.

35:46.070 --> 35:47.140
Raise your glasses.

35:48.920 --> 35:50.630
Wish you all success in your studies.

35:50.950 --> 35:52.740
-Thank you, Professor.
-Thank you, Grandpa Yu.

35:55.150 --> 35:56.030
Take it slow.

35:56.470 --> 35:57.070
Let's eat.

35:59.990 --> 36:01.680
What have you learned

36:03.150 --> 36:04.510
from this internship?

36:05.580 --> 36:06.710
Feel free to talk about it.

36:13.070 --> 36:13.630
Li Jie.

36:14.070 --> 36:15.470
Don't just eat.

36:16.320 --> 36:17.950
Tell me what you learned.

36:20.150 --> 36:21.950
What I learned recently is that

36:22.400 --> 36:23.950
when I'm facing

36:23.950 --> 36:25.680
a patient's critical situation alone,

36:25.990 --> 36:27.590
I need to be calm and decisive.

36:28.390 --> 36:29.160
I shouldn't...

36:30.320 --> 36:30.990
Alone?

36:36.030 --> 36:36.880
He Suye.

36:37.630 --> 36:39.070
You let an intern

36:39.800 --> 36:42.470
face the critical situation alone?

36:44.630 --> 36:46.360
He was on duty in the hospital that day. I...

36:46.360 --> 36:48.680
Don't tell me any objective reasons.

36:49.860 --> 36:51.530
Right, I left them to you.

36:52.240 --> 36:55.070
It wasn't just to let you teach them theoretical knowledge.

36:55.070 --> 36:57.550
What's more important is practice,

36:57.860 --> 36:59.500
especially front-line practice.

37:00.110 --> 37:00.750
Right.

37:01.200 --> 37:02.430
But you can't

37:02.840 --> 37:04.680
let him handle it alone.

37:05.720 --> 37:06.550
Got it.

37:06.850 --> 37:08.130
I'll be more careful in the future.

37:08.630 --> 37:09.800
Have some wine.

37:10.220 --> 37:11.530
Let's not talk about this now.

37:11.820 --> 37:12.570
Come on.

37:13.080 --> 37:13.770
Let's eat.

37:14.320 --> 37:15.360
Let's eat.

38:29.280 --> 38:30.920
Yesterday, I went to the clinic on your behalf,

38:31.950 --> 38:33.800
and two young ladies came in for a follow-up visit.

38:34.240 --> 38:35.630
When they saw it was me,

38:36.720 --> 38:37.760
they looked

38:37.760 --> 38:39.200
really disappointed.

38:43.830 --> 38:45.560
So the doctor she saw was you.

38:47.110 --> 38:48.720
One of them is surnamed Shen.

38:49.070 --> 38:49.990
What's her name again...

38:50.990 --> 38:51.760
Shen Xifan.

38:52.760 --> 38:53.990
She has insomnia.

38:56.430 --> 38:57.800
how's her situation this week?

38:58.070 --> 38:59.240
I checked her pulse.

38:59.400 --> 39:00.550
Her liver and kidneys are weak.

39:01.200 --> 39:01.990
But

39:02.530 --> 39:04.890
her sleep and complexion have improved.

39:04.950 --> 39:07.070
I adjusted the amount of some ingredients according to your previous prescription

39:07.070 --> 39:08.280
for another week.

39:09.430 --> 39:10.110
That's good.

39:12.320 --> 39:13.680
In the future, when you have to be absent,

39:13.680 --> 39:15.550
inform the patients in advance.

39:15.550 --> 39:17.300
Don't let them come for nothing.

39:17.510 --> 39:19.110
It's also bad for your medical ethics.

39:20.150 --> 39:21.720
I don't have her contact information.

39:21.720 --> 39:22.950
How should I inform her in advance?

39:23.320 --> 39:25.430
Patients are required to leave their phone numbers when making an appointment.

39:25.430 --> 39:27.470
You can inquire about it at the front desk.

39:28.240 --> 39:29.070
That won't do.

39:30.280 --> 39:31.800
Then when she comes for the follow-up visit next time,

39:32.430 --> 39:33.510
ask for

39:33.510 --> 39:34.470
her phone number.

39:37.720 --> 39:39.280
I like the look

39:39.800 --> 39:41.110
of this girl.

39:41.840 --> 39:43.360
She's pretty good-looking.

39:43.880 --> 39:44.880
She has good temperament,

39:45.030 --> 39:45.840
and she's quite elegant.

39:46.260 --> 39:47.530
I liked her at first sight.

39:48.630 --> 39:49.680
She's four years younger than you.

39:49.680 --> 39:51.320
You're also suitable for each other in age.

40:10.070 --> 40:12.240
That traditional Chinese medicine didn't work at all.

40:12.450 --> 40:13.090
How about you

40:13.110 --> 40:14.370
throw it away for me?

40:14.400 --> 40:15.400
What a waste that would be.

40:15.800 --> 40:16.320
Oh my god.

40:17.050 --> 40:17.780
Dr. He.

40:27.320 --> 40:27.950
Dr. He.

40:28.430 --> 40:29.880
I'll go there again for another follow-up visit next weekend.

40:30.040 --> 40:31.510
Don't stand me up again.

40:31.870 --> 40:35.570
♫No matter how much longer it is in the dark♫

40:36.110 --> 40:39.480
♫Your voice is always gentle♫
